<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Http_Response::extractHeaders does not recognize headers like "Location:<a href="http://example.com">http://example.com</a>" i.e. without a space after the "<em>:</em>".</p>

<p>To fix it, please change line 510, Zend/Http/Response.php from</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
            if (preg_match("|^([\w-]+):\s+(.+)|", $line, $m)) 
</code></pre>

<p>to</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
            if (preg_match("|^([\w-]+):\s*(.+)|", $line, $m)) 
</code></pre>

    </div>
</div>

